{
	"info": {
		"name": "WMS Order Service API",
		"description": "Order Management Microservice for the Warehouse Management System (WMS).\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders\n\n## Order Status Flow\n```\nCREATED → VALIDATED → APPROVED/PARTIALLY_APPROVED → PICKING_REQUESTED → PACKED → DISPATCHED → DELIVERED\n                    ↘ REJECTED\nAny (except DISPATCHED/DELIVERED) → CANCELLED\n```\n\n## Testing Flow\n1. Create Order\n2. Get Order by ID (auto-saves orderId)\n3. List Orders (all / by status)\n4. Validate Order (requires Inventory Service)\n5. Approve Order (FULL / PARTIAL / AUTO)\n6. Update Status (PICKING_REQUESTED → PACKED → DISPATCHED → DELIVERED)\n7. Cancel Order\n\n## Error Codes\n| Code | HTTP | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| NOT_FOUND | 404 | Resource not found |\n| BUSINESS_ERROR | 400 | Business rule violation |\n| VALIDATION_ERROR | 400 | Request validation failure |\n| EXTERNAL_SERVICE_ERROR | 502 | Inventory Service unavailable |\n| INTERNAL_ERROR | 500 | Unexpected server error |",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "orderId",
			"value": "PASTE_ORDER_UUID_HERE",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "orderId2",
			"value": "PASTE_ORDER_UUID_HERE",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Create Orders",
			"description": "Endpoints to create new orders",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Create Order (Partial Allowed)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"CUST-LK-001\",\n  \"partialAllowed\": true,\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-001\",\n      \"quantity\": 10,\n      \"unitPrice\": 250.00\n    },\n    {\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-002\",\n      \"quantity\": 5,\n      \"unitPrice\": 500.00\n    },\n    {\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-003\",\n      \"quantity\": 20,\n      \"unitPrice\": 100.00\n    }\n  ]\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "v1", "orders"]
						},
						"description": "Creates a new order with `partialAllowed = true` and 3 items.\n\n**Request Body Fields:**\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| customerId | string | ✅ | Customer identifier (cannot be blank) |\n| partialAllowed | boolean | ✅ | Whether partial fulfillment is acceptable |\n| items | array | ✅ | At least one item required |\n| items[].itemId | string | ✅ | Inventory item identifier |\n| items[].quantity | int | ✅ | Quantity (must be ≥ 1) |\n| items[].unitPrice | decimal | ❌ | Price per unit |\n\n**Response:** 201 Created with the new order including auto-generated order number.\n\nThe `orderId` collection variable is auto-set from the response."
					},
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('orderId', jsonData.id);",
									"    console.log('Order ID saved: ' + jsonData.id);",
									"    console.log('Order Number: ' + jsonData.orderNumber);",
									"}",
									"",
									"pm.test('Status code is 201 Created', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Status is CREATED', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('CREATED');",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Order number format ORD-YYYY-NNNNNN', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.orderNumber).to.match(/^ORD-\\d{4}-\\d{6}$/);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Has 3 items', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.items).to.be.an('array').with.lengthOf(3);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Total amount is calculated correctly', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    // (10 * 250) + (5 * 500) + (20 * 100) = 2500 + 2500 + 2000 = 7000",
									"    pm.expect(Number(jsonData.totalAmount)).to.eql(7000);",
									"});"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "201 - Order Created Successfully",
							"status": "Created",
							"code": 201,
							"header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
							"body": "{\n  \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890\",\n  \"orderNumber\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n  \"customerId\": \"CUST-LK-001\",\n  \"status\": \"CREATED\",\n  \"partialAllowed\": true,\n  \"totalAmount\": 7000.00,\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-02-15T11:00:00+05:30\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-02-15T11:00:00+05:30\",\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901\",\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-001\",\n      \"requestedQty\": 10,\n      \"approvedQty\": 0,\n      \"unitPrice\": 250.00\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012\",\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-002\",\n      \"requestedQty\": 5,\n      \"approvedQty\": 0,\n      \"unitPrice\": 500.00\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d4e5f6a7-b8c9-0123-defa-234567890123\",\n      \"itemId\": \"ITEM-003\",\n      \"requestedQty\": 20,\n      \"approvedQty\": 0,\n      \"unitPrice\": 100.00\n    }\n  ]\n}"
						}
					]
				},
