							"path": ["api", "v1", "orders"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "status",
									"value": "CREATED",
									"description": "Filter by status. Values: CREATED, VALIDATED, APPROVED, PARTIALLY_APPROVED, REJECTED, CANCELLED, PICKING_REQUESTED, PACKED, DISPATCHED, DELIVERED"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Returns orders filtered by status.\n\n**Query Parameter:**\n| Param | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| status | enum | ❌ | Order status filter |\n\n**Available Status Values:**\n- `CREATED` — Newly created\n- `VALIDATED` — Validated against inventory\n- `APPROVED` — Fully approved\n- `PARTIALLY_APPROVED` — Partially approved\n- `REJECTED` — Rejected (insufficient stock)\n- `CANCELLED` — Cancelled by user\n- `PICKING_REQUESTED` — Picking requested in warehouse\n- `PACKED` — Items packed\n- `DISPATCHED` — Order dispatched\n- `DELIVERED` — Order delivered (final)"
					},
